article_title: Iconic Walgreens Shedding 'WAG' Ticker Symbol, Moving To Nasdaq

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: Walgreen Co. (WAG), which is acquiring the remaining shares of European drugstore giant Alliance Boots that it does not own, said the new holding company’s stock will trade on The Nasdaq Stock Market only once the deal closes, shedding its 87-year-old “WAG” ticker symbol.
